{"tid":1826130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"The House just voted to kick-start Trump’s impeachment trial","createTime":"2020-01-16T01:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T01:16:07.000Z","uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a32ff003a09958759892a585ce1db619b2d7f6","tid":1826130,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T01:13:53.000Z","msg":"They&rsquo;re officially sending the articles of impeachment over, meaning the trial can now begin.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ecYi_I_Bb33omd3dpmwO3qXT3aY=/0x0:5568x3712/1820x1213/filters:focal(2339x1411:3229x2301):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/66105778/GettyImages_1193889762.0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FecYi_I_Bb33omd3dpmwO3qXT3aY%3D%2F0x0%3A5568x3712%2F1820x1213%2Ffilters%3Afocal%282339x1411%3A3229x2301%29%3Aformat%28webp%29%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_image%2Fimage%2F66105778%2FGettyImages_1193889762.0.jpg&h=f4b53f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe House of Representatives voted Wednesday to send the articles of impeachment against President Donald Trump over to the Senate &mdash; finally taking the procedural step necessary for Trump&rsquo;s trial to begin.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vox.com/2020/1/15/21065810/who-are-the-impeachment-managers-pelosi-senate-trial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2F2020%2F1%2F15%2F21065810%2Fwho-are-the-impeachment-managers-pelosi-senate-trial&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=1b2c1d56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vox.com/2020/1/15/21065810/who-are-the-impeachment-managers-pelosi-senate-trial</a>"},{"pid":"769cdf5d8535a0e24f41a91e8c7d97a96a21dff2","tid":1826130,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T01:16:07.000Z","msg":"個人認為 trump trump 畀人搞嘅主要原因：<br />\n<br />\n1．